quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,14,"Mubarwanye kugira ngo Allah abahane akoresheje amaboko yanyu, abakoze isoni ndetse namwe abahe intsinzi, kandi imitima y’abemeramana ayikize (agahinda)"
  9,15,"Ndetse anakure uburakari mu mitima yabo. Allah yakira ukwicuza k'uwo ashaka. Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  9,16,"Ese (mwe abemeramana) mwibwira ko muzarekwa (mutyo) Allah atagaragaje abaharaniye inzira ye muri mwe, ndetse bakaba bataragize inshuti ibindi bitari Allah n’intumwa ye ndetse n’abemeramana? Kandi Allah azi byimazeyo ibyo mukora"
  9,17,"Ntibikwiye ko ababangikanyamana basura (basengera mu) misigiti ya Allah, kandi ubwabo bishinja ubuhakanyi. Abo ibikorwa byabo byabaye imfabusa, kandi bazaba mu muriro ubuziraherezo"
  9,18,"Mu by’ukuri abita ku misigiti ya Allah ni ba bandi bemeye Allah n'umunsi w'imperuka, bagahozaho iswala, bagatanga amaturo ndetse ntibagire undi batinya utari Allah. Birashoboka ko abo bari mu bayobotse"
  9,19,"Ese (igikorwa cyo) kwicira inyota abakora umutambagiro mutagatifu (Hijat) no kwita ku Musigiti Mutagatifu (Kabat), mubigereranya n’ibikorwa n’uwemeye Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka akanaharanira inzira ya Allah? Ntibashobora kureshya imbere ya Allah! Kandi Allah ntayobora abanyamahugu"
  9,20,"Ba bandi bemeye bakimukira (i Madina) ndetse bakanaharanira inzira ya Allah bakoresheje imitungo yabo na bo ubwabo, bafite urwego ruhambaye kwa Allah. Kandi abo ni bo batsinze"